{
  "stem": "24111.8",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They abandoned Amir.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Amir was-- the kibbutz turned into an [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, you know, the kibbutzniks, which were highly idealistically when I was there and shared everything, suddenly wanted to have more individual ownership of the land.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they started to split up into-- now it's-- they [? made ?] an-- it is not an collective anymore.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After the war, I went to Gedera and started to work for the-- for the [? fledglingly ?] small Israeli Air Force.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was very close with the president of the-- of Israel today, Chaim Weizmann.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ezer Weizman.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Chaim Weizmann was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Ezer Weizman, which was in the Air Force at my time, and he flew Piper-- Piper Cubs.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I went into the Air Force as a civilian.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I worked in Tel Nof in the engine overhauls.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But by 1951, I left Israel, and I came to the United States.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And because of my experience with the Air Force, I went here to the Academy of Aeronautics.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I graduated in 1957, and then I worked for 24 years for American Airlines.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But the beginning of my career, actually, the airline industries in Israel.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, out of a few reasons which compelled me to leave.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I came-- and I was a real idealist.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was a real Zionist.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was an-- a youngster of perhaps 18, which went into an-- into an kibbutz which had the idea of building up the land, returning the land, which was not very productive when we got it, back to the original states of thousands of years, whatever, cedar trees and so on.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I tried-- I tried my very best.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I joined the Palmah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I-- I fought in the-- in the War of Independence.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I never took any money.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
